summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Water Department authorizing the sale and conveyance by Quit Claim Deed of a portion of real property commonly known as the Lake Youngs Aqueduct Right-of-Way (LYA R/W) located in Section 13, Township 22 North, Range 5 East, W.M., King County, Washington, to Gustaf C. Anderson, Freda M. Hamlin, and Andrew Anderson, each as their separate estate.
